islang kaum beachtete frühneuzeitliche Gerichtsakten, auf Ratsprotokolle und Judenschafts-Akten, die im zweiten Teil des Werkes thematisch erschlossen werden.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aJewish ghettoszGermanyzFrankfurt am MainxHistoryy17th century. 0aJewszGermanyzFrankfurt am MainxSocial life and customsy17th century. 4aFrühe Neuzeit. 4aJüdische Gemeinde in Frankfurt a.M. 7aHISTORY / Jewish.2bisacsh  aEarly Modern Age.  aJewish Community in Frankfurt a.M.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Theology and Religious Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110638165oZDB-23-GTR08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2010z9783110233544oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET PHILOSOPHIE UND GESCHICHTE 2010z9783110233612oZDB-23-DGE0 cprintz978311023157140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311023158840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110231588423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110231588/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGEb2010  aZDB-23-DGGb2010  aZDB-23-GTRc2000d2014